  localhost : target (see config.json AND EDIT IT)
  smi...    : ...
  oeb...    : ...
  0         : start index
  2         : number of pilots
  10        : number of tasks per pilot (== number of compute nodes)
  100       : number of samples per task

next index (next run) starts at 'idx_start + n_pilots * n_tasks * n_samples'


